m reflecting the everyday life of Hong Kong people. He is well known for using amateur actors (such as Sam Lee in Made in Hong Kong, Wong Yau-Nam in Hollywood Hong Kong) in his films. His name became familiar to many Hong Kongers only after the success of the 1997 film Made in Hong Kong, which earned many local and international awards.","name":"Fruit Chan","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"프룻 첸","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"（1959年4月15日出生于中国广东），香港第二波独立编剧、电影制片人和制片人，以其反映香港人日常生活的电影风格而闻名。他以在电影中使用业余演员而闻名（例如《香港制造》中的李家超、《香港好莱坞》中的黄耀南）。直到1997年电影《香港制造》大获成功后，他的名字才为许多香港人所熟悉，该电影赢得了许多本地和国际奖项。\n\n2007年8月22日，成龙宣布将拍摄一部以李小龙早年为主题的电影，具体来说，华语电影《九龙城》将由吴宇森的制片人张国荣监制。这部电影将以 1950 年代的香港为背景。\n\nChan 的作品包括榴莲榴莲。此外，Stanley Kwan表示，他正在与Lee的家人交谈，以制作一部关于已故动作电影偶像的电影。此外，今年4月，中国官方媒体宣布，其国家电视台开始拍摄一部关于李小龙的40集电视连续剧，为2008年北京夏季奥运会宣传中国文化。","name":"陈果","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"（1959 年 4 月 15 日出生於中國廣東），香港第二波獨立編劇、電影製片人和製片人，以其反映香港人日常生活的電影風格而聞名。他以在電影中使用業餘演員而聞名（例如《香港製造》中的李家超、《香港好萊塢》中的黃耀南）。直到 1997 年電影《香港製造》大獲成功後，他的名字才為許多香港人所熟悉，該電影贏得了許多本地和國際獎項。\n\n2007 年 8 月 22 日，成龍宣佈將拍攝一部以李小龍早年為主題的電影，具體來説，華語電影《九龍城》將由吳宇森的製片人張國榮監製。這部電影將以 1950 年代的香港為背景。\n\nChan 的作品包括榴蓮榴蓮。此外，Stanley Kwan 表示，他正在與 Lee 的家人交談，以製作一部關於已故動作電影偶像的電影。此外，今年 4 月，中國官方媒體宣佈，其國家電視台開始拍攝一部關於李小龍的 40 集電視聯續劇，為 2008 年北京夏季奧運會宣傳中國文化。","name":"陳果","primary":true}}]}},"tv_274226_detail_vi-VN":{"at":1774373038942,"data":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/dRF27vTf6v387KzP9l0XBLCAUkG.jpg","created_by":[],"episode_run_time":[],"first_air_date":"2026-03-05","genres":[{"id":18,"name":"Phim Chính Kịch"}],"homepage":"https://v.qq.com/x/cover/mzc00200noenxzb.html","id":274226,"in_production":false,"languages":["zh"],"last_air_date":"2026-03-11","last_episode_to_air":{"id":7008935,"name":"Episode 24","overview":"","vote_average":0,"vote_count":0,"air_date":"2026-03-11","episode_number":24,"episode_type":"finale","production_code":"","runtime":null,"season_number":1,"show_id":274226,"still_path":null},"name":"Trâm Khoá Tình","next_episode_to_air":null,"networks":[{"id":2007,"logo_path":"/6Lfll43wYG2eyereOBjpYFRSGs4.png","name":"Tencent Video","origin_country":"CN"}],"number_of_episodes":24,"number_of_seasons":1,"origin_country":["CN"],"original_language":"zh","original_name":"锁簪","overview":"Bách Hiểu sơn trang tọa lạc giữa chốn rừng sâu chướng khí ngút ngàn, suốt mấy chục năm qua luôn là một vùng cấm địa bí ẩn. Thế nhưng, ngay trước thềm Bách Hiểu dạ yến, trang chủ Bách Hiểu sơn trang lại đột nhiên mất tích một cách khó hiểu. Giữa lúc cấp bách, tử tù Diệp Lễ đã tự nguyện đứng ra, bắt tay cùng bổ khoái Đại Lý Tự là Hóa Càn Khôn để điều tra chân tướng. Cả hai đã xả thân nhập cuộc, xông pha vào chốn hiểm nguy, để rồi vô tình vén lên bức màn che giấu một âm mưu kinh thiên động địa ẩn sau sơn trang…","popularity":0.5224,"poster_path":"/qyvH9D0mxaf9vcy1yAvAxnq2hzC.jpg","production_companies":[],"production_countries":[{"iso_3166_1":"CN","name":"China"}],"seasons":[{"air_date":"2026-03-05","episode_count":24,"id":423362,"name":"Season 1","overview":"","poster_path":null,"season_number":1,"vote_average":0}],"spoken_languages":[{"english_name":"Mandarin","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话"}],"status":"Ended","tagline":"","type":"Scripted","vote_average":0,"vote_count":0}},"person_357551_translations":{"at":1774373052664,"data":{"id":357551,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Actress known for appearing on TV shows like The Paul Reiser Show and Curb Your Enthusiasm as well as Off-Broadway productions. In 2014, she began playing Sarah Pfefferman on the Amazon comedy-drama series Transparent.","name":"Amy 